<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，杰克把米可牵了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一起慢慢地向镇上走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走着走着，突然一个声音响了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，杰克！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一位奇怪的老爷爷向他挥了挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他蓝色的眼睛像星星一样闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他怎么知道我的名字？” 杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老爷爷走过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他围着奶牛跳起了舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“米可是一头非常好的奶牛。” 老爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要带它去哪儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要带它去市场。” 杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它是一头好奶牛，但是我必须卖掉它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？” 老爷爷的眼睛亮了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要卖掉它？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老爷爷又跳起了舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天是我的幸运日！” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也是你的幸运日！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老爷爷伸出一只手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克眨了眨眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的手里有五个白色的小东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些……是豆子吗？” 杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老爷爷笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然是豆子——神奇的豆子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克又看了看豆子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“神奇的豆子？” 杰克心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看起来就是普通的豆子呀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们做个交易吧。” 老爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我用这五颗豆子换你的米可。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
